 1) Phase1_Requirements_Implementation_Map.pdf  ✅ (Best proof + safest)

*What it contains (demo layout):*

*Module: Learning History*

* *Requirement:* Track user learning progress per lesson + timestamps
* *Routes:*

  * POST /api/v1/learning-history
  * GET /api/v1/learning-history/:userId
* *Route file:* routes/learningHistory.routes.js
* *Controller:* controllers/learningHistory.controller.js
* *Service:* services/learningHistory.service.js
* *Model:* models/LearningHistory.model.js
* *Key validations:* userId exists, lessonId valid, upsert logic

*Module: Quiz Generation & Attempts*

* Routes:

  * POST /api/v1/quiz/generate
  * POST /api/v1/quiz/attempts
  * GET /api/v1/quiz/attempts/:userId
* Files: routes/quiz.routes.js → controllers/quiz.controller.js → services/quiz.service.js
* Models: Quiz.model.js, QuizAttempt.model.js

*Module: Chat History + Session Link*

* Routes:

  * POST /api/v1/chat/message
  * GET /api/v1/chat/sessions/:sessionId/messages
* Models: ChatSession.model.js, ChatMessage.model.js

➡️ *This doc must include “exact file paths”* (client asked this).

