### 2) DB_Schema_Overview.pdf ✅ (safe proof)

*What it contains (demo):*

* A small diagram + fields list (no full code needed)

Example:

*LearningHistory*

* user: ObjectId(ref User)
* lessonId: ObjectId
* progress: Number
* lastAccessedAt: Date
* Index: { user, lessonId } unique

*QuizAttempt*

* user: ObjectId
* quizId: ObjectId
* answers: []
* score: Number
* createdAt

*ChatSession*

* user: ObjectId
* sessionKey: String
* createdAt

*ChatMessage*

* session: ObjectId(ref ChatSession)
* sender: enum(user/system)
* message: String
* createdAt
